        "heading": "1. Standard Scope and Purpose; 3.4 Antenatal Care; 3.4.1 Routine Antenatal Care",
        "locator": "pages 2–5",
        "evidence_summary": "Defines routine antenatal documentation, risk review at every visit, history and record review, patient concerns, shared decisions, counselling, care plans, and high-risk referral boundaries."
