        "heading": "Appendix 1 — Routine Antenatal Screening and Care",
        "locator": "pages 8–12",
        "evidence_summary": "Specifies gestation-linked weight, blood pressure, urine dipstick, fetal heart, fundal height, fetal movement, laboratory, ultrasound, glucose-screening, counselling, and follow-up documentation."
      },
